                    <div class="node node-news node-promoted node-sticky node-teaser clearfix" id="node-3333">
                     <h2>
                      <a href="/policy-place/policy-update-list">
                       Policy Update List
                      </a>
                     </h2>
                     <div class="content">
                      <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
                       <div class="field-items">
                        <div class="field-item even">
                         <p>
                          If you would like to be informed of policy updates, please
                          <a href="mailto:sympa@utlists.utexas.edu?subject=sub%20policy_update">
                           Subscribe
                          </a>
                          to Policy Update (simply click “Send” when the email message opens;
